'''Encyklopedia Internautica''' is a Polish [[Internet encyclopedia]] based on the ''Popularna Encyklopedia Powszechna'' (Popular Universal Encyclopedia) or Pinnex. It is freely accessible on the pages of [[Interia]], Poland's third largest [[internet portal]]. As of 2006 the Encyklopedia Internautica had more than 120,000 entries.

==External links==
* [http://www.encyklopedia.interia.pl Encyklopedia Internautica, homepage]

